---
// Counters — 3 key stats
// ⚠️ NO "24h risposta" — regola brand memory.md 12 mag 2026
---
<section class="bg-cream py-24 md:py-32 relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-12" data-reveal>
      <span class="w-8 h-px bg-ink"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow text-ink/70">numeri che contano</span>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 md:gap-8 mb-12">
      <div data-reveal>
        <div class="big-num font-display-tight text-[18vw] md:text-[10vw] text-ink leading-none">
          <span class="counter" data-target="30000">0</span><span class="text-orange">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold">articoli a catalogo</div>
        <div class="text-ink/60 text-sm">…e ogni giorno se ne aggiungono</div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal>
        <div class="big-num font-display-tight text-[18vw] md:text-[10vw] text-ink leading-none">
          <span class="counter" data-target="12">0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold">anni di stampa</div>
        <div class="text-ink/60 text-sm">attivi dal 2014, ne abbiamo viste di tutti i Pantone</div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal>
        <div class="big-num font-display-tight text-[18vw] md:text-[10vw] text-ink leading-none">
          <span class="counter" data-target="7">0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold">giorni · consegna</div>
        <div class="text-ink/60 text-sm">dalla conferma al vostro logo su tutto</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-ink/10 pt-8 max-w-3xl">
      <p class="font-display-tight text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ink leading-tight">
        <span class="underline-orange">…ok, davvero tanti.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
